        '<div style=\"color: black\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: \n      18px;\">Result:</span></strong></p>\n<p>You have individual symptoms that can also occur with COVID-19.\n<br>You are not aware of having been in close contact with a person who has tested positive for COVID-19.\n<br>You are unlikely to have been infected with the new coronavirus.\n</p></div>',
        '<div style=\"color: black\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: \n      18px;\">Empfehlung:</span></strong></p>\n<p>\nSie haben bei der Arbeit Kontakt zu besonders gefährdeten Personen. In diesem Umfeld gelten besondere Massnahmen. </p>\n<p>\nBefolgen Sie weiterhin die Hygiene- und Verhaltensregeln der Kampagne <a href=\"http://www.bag.admin.ch/so-schuetzen-wir-uns\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">«So schützen wir uns»</a>. Bitte achten Sie insbesondere bei der Arbeit auf eine strikte Handhygiene.\n<p>\nWenden Sie sich an Ihre Ärztin bzw. Ihren Arzt oder eine Gesundheitseinrichtung, falls die Symptome Sie beunruhigen oder sich verschlimmern. \n</p>\n<p>\nMachen Sie diesen Check erneut, sobald weitere Symptome dazukommen. Sie erhalten dann eine der Situation angepasste Empfehlung.\n</p></div>\n',
        '<div style=\"color: black\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: \n      18px;\">Recommandation :</span></strong></p>\n<p>\nVous êtes en contact avec des personnes vulnérables sur votre lieu de travail. Vous devez donc prendre des mesures particulières.\n</p>\n<p>\nContinuez à suivre les règles d’hygiène et de conduite de la campagne <a href=\"http://www.bag.admin.ch/voici-comment-nous-proteger\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">«Voici comment nous protéger»</a>. Faites particulièrement attention à une hygiène des mains stricte sur le lieu de travail.\n<p>\nSurveillez votre état de santé. Adressez-vous à votre médecin ou à un établissement de santé si les symptômes vous préoccupent ou empirent.\n</p>\n<p>\nRefaites ce test dès que vous développez de nouveaux symptômes. Vous obtiendrez ainsi une recommandation adaptée à votre situation.\n</p></div>\n',
        '<div style=\"\"color: black\"\"><p><strong><span style=\"\"font-size: \n      18px;\"\">Raccomandazione:</span></strong></p>\n<p>\nSul lavoro è a contatto con persone particolarmente a rischio. In questa situazione si applicano misure particolari. \n</p>\n<p>\nContinui a seguire le regole di igiene e di comportamento della campagna <a href=\"\"http://www.bag.admin.ch/cosi-ci-proteggiamo\"\" rel=\"\"noopener noreferrer\"\" target=\"\"_blank\"\">«Così ci proteggiamo»</a>. Si prega di prestare particolare attenzione alla rigorosa igiene delle mani sul lavoro.\n</p>\n<p>\nSorvegli il Suo stato di salute. Se i sintomi La preoccupano o si aggravano, si rivolga al Suo medico o a un’istituzione sanitaria.\n</p>\n<p>\nRipeta l’autovalutazione non appena dovessero comparire altri sintomi. Il sistema Le fornirà una nuova raccomandazione adeguata alla Sua situazione.\n</p></div>\n',
        '<div style=\"\"color: black\"\"><p><strong><span style=\"\"font-size: \n      18px;\"\">Recommendation:</span></strong></p>\n<p>\nAt work you are in contact with people who are at especially high risk. Special measures apply in these situations.\n</p>\n<p>\nContinue to follow the rules on hygiene and social distancing in the <a href=\"\"http://www.bag.admin.ch/protect-yourself-and-others\"\" rel=\"\"noopener noreferrer\"\" target=\"\"_blank\"\">«Protect yourself and others»</a> campaign. Please pay particular attention to a strict hand hygiene at work.\n</p>\n<p>Monitor your state of health. Contact your doctor or a health centre if your symptoms are worrying you or worsen.\n</p>\n<p>\nGo through this check again as soon as you have additional symptoms. You will then receive a recommendation adapted to your situation.\n</p></div>'),

